            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Welcome, Champion! I've been waiting, mwahahaha!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Uh...huh? Champion?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I need to thank you. I've been in bad shape for a long time, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Thanks to you, I've fully recovered to my original condition! Thank you!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "And, it is not like me to keep losing!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "So, I propose a revenge battle! You'll certainly accept it, won't you!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Umm, is this something that I should really accept?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x25,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Of course. And I am a challenger with an unyielding soul!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "It is a bit of a heartwrenching story that I have to knock my benefactor down to the ground..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "But I will defeat you! For that is my duty as the former champion!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I understand, but I won't lose either!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x56,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Hmhmhm, good answer. That is why you are my rivaaal!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x57,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Now, let's go all-out. Today, we'll‐"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Okay, okay, okay, then let's just start."
